# Pok√©mon Cards API - REST Endpoints

### Get all cards
GET http://localhost:3000/cards

---

### Get card by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/cards/{id}

Example:
GET http://localhost:3000/cards/689b0d295b4433784ce8f96f

---

### Create a new card
POST http://localhost:3000/cards
Content-Type: application/json

Request Body:
{
  "name": "Charizard",
  "set": "Base Set",
  "rarity": "Holo Rare",
  "number": "4/102",
  "release_year": 1999,
  "price_usd": 250.00
}

---

### Update a card
PUT http://localhost:3000/cards/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

Request Body:
{
  "name": "Charizard",
  "set": "Base Set",
  "rarity": "Holo Rare",
